00:34:10.630 --> 00:34:11.880
Or, I think it should
be slower.

00:34:14.580 --> 00:34:18.010
Design does have these
fundamental principles.

00:34:18.010 --> 00:34:20.469
Various usability heuristics,
things that we've learned

00:34:20.469 --> 00:34:22.515
